NAME: Gift of Arthas
SPECIAL: If an enemy strikes the imbiber, the attacker has a 30% chance of being inflicted with disease that increases their damage taken by 8 for 3 min.

NAME: Greater Arcane Protection Potion
SPECIAL: Absorbs 1950 to 3250 arcane damage.

NAME: Greater Fire Protection Potion
SPECIAL: Absorbs 1950 to 3250 fire damage.

NAME: Greater Frost Protection Potion
SPECIAL: Absorbs 1950 to 3250 frost damage.

NAME: Greater Nature Protection Potion
SPECIAL: Absorbs 1950 to 3250 nature damage.

NAME: Greater Shadow Protection Potion
SPECIAL: Absorbs 1950 to 3250 shadow damage.

NAME: Limited Invulnerability Potion
SPECIAL: Imbiber is immune to physical attacks for the next 6 sec.

NAME: Restorative Potion
SPECIAL: Removes 1 magic, curse, poison or disease effect on you every 5 seconds for 30 seconds

NAME: Free Action Potion
SPECIAL: Makes you immune to Stun and Movement Impairing effects for the next 30 sec.

NAME: Concentration Aura
SPECIAL: Gives a 35% chance of ignoring spell interruption when damaged to all party members within 30 yards.

NAME: Sanctity Aura
SPECIAL: Increases Holy damage done by party members within 30 yards by 10%.

NAME: Defensive Stance
SPECIAL: Increases threat generated.

NAME: Challenging Roar
SPECIAL: Forces all nearby enemies to focus attacks on you for 6 sec.

NAME: Fade
SPECIAL: Fade out, discouraging enemies from attacking you for 10 sec.

NAME: Feign Death
SPECIAL: Feign death which may trick enemies into ignoring you.

NAME: Challenging Shout
SPECIAL: Forces all nearby enemies to focus attacks on you for 6 sec.

NAME: Omen of Clarity
SPECIAL: Imbues the Druid with natural energy. Each of the Druid's melee attacks has a chance of causing the caster to enter a Clearcasting state. The Clearcasting state reduces the Mana, Rage or Energy cost of your next damage or healing spell or offensive ability by 100%.

NAME: Power Word: Shield
SPECIAL: Draws on the soul of the party member to shield them, absorbing 942 damage. Lasts 30 sec. While the shield holds, spellcasting will not be interrupted by damage.

NAME: Feedback
SPECIAL: The priest becomes surrounded with anti-magic energy. Any successful spell cast against the priest will burn 105 of the attacker's Mana, causing 1 Shadow damage for each point of Mana burned.

NAME: Elune’s Grace
SPECIAL: Reduces ranged damage taken by 95 and increases chance to dodge by 10% for 15 sec.

NAME: Seal of Righteousness
SPECIAL: Fills the Paladin with holy spirit for 30 sec, granting each melee attack an additional 22 to 75 Holy damage. Slower weapons cause more Holy damage per swing. Only one Seal can be active on the Paladin at any one time. Unleashing this Seal's energy will cause 170 to 187 Holy damage to an enemy.

NAME: Seal of the Crusader
SPECIAL: Fills the Paladin with the spirit of a crusader for 30 sec, granting 326 melee attack power. The Paladin also attacks 40% faster, but deals less damage with each attack. Only one Seal can be active on the Paladin at any one time. Unleashing this Seal's energy will judge an enemy for 10 sec, increasing Holy damage taken by up to 140. Your melee strikes will refresh the spell's duration.

NAME: Seal of Light
SPECIAL: Fills the Paladin with divine light for 30 sec, giving each melee attack a chance to heal the Paladin for 94. Only one Seal can be active on the Paladin at any one time. Unleashing this Seal's energy will judge an enemy for 10 sec, granting melee attacks made against the judged enemy a chance of healing the attacker for 61.

NAME: Seal of Wisdom
SPECIAL: Fills the Paladin with divine wisdom for 30 sec, giving each melee attack a chance to restore 90 of the Paladin's mana. Only one Seal can be active on the Paladin at any one time. Unleashing this Seal's energy will judge an enemy for 10 sec, granting attacks and spells used against the judged enemy a chance to restore 59 mana to the attacker.

NAME: Righteous Fury
SPECIAL: Increases the threat generated by your Holy attacks by 60%.

NAME: Greater Blessing of Light
SPECIAL: increasing the effects of Holy Light spells used on the target by up to 400 and the effect Flash of Light spells used on the target by up to 115.

NAME: Greater Blessing of Salvation
SPECIAL: reducing the amount of all threat generated by 30%

NAME: Greater Blessing of Kings
SPECIAL: increasing total stats by 10%

NAME: Seal of Command
SPECIAL: Gives the Paladin a chance to deal additional Holy damage equal to 70% of normal weapon damage. Only one Seal can be active on the Paladin at any one time. Lasts 30 sec. Unleashing this Seal's energy will judge an enemy, instantly causing 169 to 186 Holy damage, 339 to 373 if the target is stunned or incapacitated.

NAME: Amplify Magic
SPECIAL: Amplifies magic used against the targeted party member, increasing damage taken from spells by up to 75 and healing spells by up to 150.

NAME: Dampen Magic
SPECIAL: Dampens magic used against the targeted party member, decreasing damage taken from spells by up to 90 and healing spells by up to 180.

NAME: Mana Shield
SPECIAL: Absorbs 570 physical damage, draining mana instead.  Drains 2 mana per damage absorbed.

NAME: Fire Ward
SPECIAL: Absorbs 920 Fire damage.

NAME: Mage Armor
SPECIAL: Increases your resistance to all magic by 15 and allows 30% of your mana regeneration to continue while casting.

NAME: Frost Ward
SPECIAL: Absorbs 920 Frost damage.

NAME: Combustion
SPECIAL: When activated, this spell causes each of your Fire damage spell hits to increase your critical strike chance with Fire damage spells by 10%. This effect lasts until you have caused 3 critical strikes with Fire spells.

NAME: Ice Block
SPECIAL: You become encased in a block of ice, protecting you from all physical attacks and spells for 10 sec, but during that time you cannot attack, move or cast spells.

NAME: Arcane Power
SPECIAL: When activated, your spells deal 30% more damage while costing 30% more mana to cast.

NAME: Presence of Mind
SPECIAL: When activated, your next Mage spell with a casting time less than 10 sec becomes an instant cast spell.

NAME: Ice Barrier
SPECIAL: Instantly shields you, absorbing 826 damage. Lasts 1 min. While the shield holds, spells will not be interrupted.

NAME: Shadow Ward
SPECIAL: Absorbs 920 shadow damage.

NAME: Amplify Curse
SPECIAL: Increases the effect of your next Curse of Weakness or Curse of Agony by 50%, or your next Curse of Exhaustion by 20%.

NAME: Fel Domination
SPECIAL: Your next Imp, Voidwalker, Succubus, Incubus, or Felhunter Summon spell has its casting time reduced by 5.5 sec and its Mana cost reduced by 50%.

NAME: Demonic Sacrifice
SPECIAL: When activated, sacrifices your summoned demon to grant you an effect that lasts 30 min. The effect is canceled if any Demon is summoned. Imp: Increases your Fire damage by 15%. Voidwalker: Restores 3% of total Health every 4 sec. Succubus/Incubus: Increases your Shadow damage by 15%. Felhunter: Restores 2% of total Mana every 4 sec.

NAME: Soul Link
SPECIAL: When active, 30% of all damage taken by the caster is taken by your Imp, Voidwalker, Succubus, Incubus, or Felhunter demon instead. In addition, both the demon and master will inflict 3% more damage.

NAME: Rapid Fire
SPECIAL: Increases ranged attack speed by 40%

NAME: Deterrence
SPECIAL: When activated, increases your Dodge and Parry chance by 25%

NAME: Bestial Wrath
SPECIAL: Send your pet into a rage causing 50% additional damage for 18 sec. While enraged, the beast does not feel pity or remorse or fear and it cannot be stopped unless killed.

NAME: Evasion
SPECIAL: The rogue's dodge chance will increase by 50% for 15 sec.

NAME: Slice and Dice
SPECIAL: Finishing move that increases melee attack speed by 30%.  Lasts longer per combo point:

NAME: Adrenaline Rush
SPECIAL: Increases your Energy regeneration rate by 100% for 15 sec.

NAME: Blade Flurry
SPECIAL: Increases your attack speed by 20%. In addition, attacks strike an additional nearby opponent.

NAME: Cold Blood
SPECIAL: When activated, increases the critical strike chance of your next Sinister Strike, Backstab, Ambush, or Eviscerate by 100%.

NAME: Shield Wall
SPECIAL: Reduces the damage taken from melee attacks, ranged attacks and spells by 75% for 10 sec.

NAME: Recklessness
SPECIAL: The warrior will cause critical hits with most attacks and will be immune to Fear effects for the next 15 sec, but all damage taken is increased by 20%

NAME: Shield Block
SPECIAL: Increases chance to block by 75% for 5 sec, but will only block 1 attack.

NAME: Bloodrage
SPECIAL: Generates 10 rage at the cost of health, and then generates an additional 10 rage over 10 sec.

NAME: Berserker Rage
SPECIAL: becoming immune to Fear and Incapacitate effects and generating extra rage when taking damage.

NAME: Retaliation
SPECIAL: Instantly counterattack any enemy that strikes you in melee for 15 sec. Melee attacks made from behind cannot be counterattacked. A maximum of 30 attacks will cause retaliation.

NAME: Sweeping Strikes
SPECIAL: Your next 5 melee attacks strike an additional nearby opponent.

NAME: Death Wish
SPECIAL: When activated, increases your physical damage by 20% and makes you immune to Fear effects, but lowers your armor and all resistances by 20%.

NAME: Last Stand
SPECIAL: When activated, this ability temporarily grants you 30% of your maximum hit points for 20 seconds.

NAME: Stoneform
SPECIAL: While active, grants immunity to Bleed, Poison, and Disease effects. In addition, Armor increased by 10%.

NAME: Instant Poison VI
SPECIAL: Each strike has a 20% chance of poisoning the enemy which instantly inflicts 112 to 148 Nature damage.

NAME: Wound Poison IV
SPECIAL: Each strike has a 30% chance of poisoning the enemy, reducing all healing effects used on them by 135 for 15 sec.

NAME: Deadly Poison V
SPECIAL: Coats a weapon with poison that lasts for 30 minutes. Each strike has a 30% chance of poisoning the enemy for 136 Nature damage over 12 sec. Stacks up to 5 times on a single target.

NAME: Shadowmeld
SPECIAL: Activate to slip into the shadows, reducing the chance for enemies to detect your presence.

NAME: Fiery Aura
SPECIAL: When struck in combat inflicts 13 Fire damage to the attacker.

NAME: Bonereavers Edge
SPECIAL: Your attacks ignore 700 of your enemies' armor for 10 sec. This effect stacks up to 3 times.

NAME: Immolation
SPECIAL: Deals 5 Fire damage to anyone who strikes you with a melee attack.

NAME: Thorns Dmg 3
SPECIAL: When struck in combat inflicts 3 Arcane damage to the attacker.

NAME: Crest of Retribution
SPECIAL: Deals 5 to 35 damage every time you block.

NAME: Heart of the Scale
SPECIAL: Increases Fire Resistance by 20 and deals 20 Fire damage to anyone who strikes you with a melee attack

NAME: Mark of the Dragon Lord
SPECIAL: A protective mana shield surrounds the caster absorbing 500 damage. While the shield holds, increases mana regeneration by 22 every 5 sec

NAME: Felstriker
SPECIAL: All attacks are guaranteed to land and will be critical strikes for the next 3 sec.

NAME: Bonespike
SPECIAL: Deals 60 to 90 damage when you are the victim of a critical melee strike.

NAME: Burst of Knowledge
SPECIAL: Reduces mana cost of all spells by 100

NAME: Second Wind
SPECIAL: Restores 30 mana every 1 sec

NAME: Force of Will
SPECIAL: When struck in combat has a 1% chance of reducing all melee damage taken by 25

NAME: Thorns
SPECIAL: When struck in combat inflicts 3 Arcane damage to the attacker.
